---
/**
 * ai-agents/0004 · Shared arrowhead marker defs.
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from the top of <body> in
 * docs/ai-agents/lessons/0004-agent-systems-and-production.html. In the source
 * this is a single 0×0 absolutely-positioned <svg> holding the four <marker>
 * defs (#arw, #arwA, #arwG, #arwR) that Fig1/Fig2/Fig3 reference via
 * marker-end="url(#…)". It lives as a component (rendered ONCE, before the
 * figures) so the marker ids resolve document-wide and the figures stay byte-
 * for-byte verbatim — inline SVG with kebab-case attrs is unreliable in MDX.
 */
---

<svg width="0" height="0" style="position:absolute" aria-hidden="true"
    ><defs>
        <marker
            id="arw"
            viewBox="0 0 10 10"
            refX="8.5"
            refY="5"
            markerWidth="7"
            markerHeight="7"
            orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#6b675f"></path></marker
        >
        <marker
            id="arwA"
            viewBox="0 0 10 10"
            refX="8.5"
            refY="5"
            markerWidth="7"
            markerHeight="7"
            orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#7a1f12"></path></marker
        >
        <marker
